description: This notification is sent when a CF Card is hot swapped in.
objects.test: $SNMPTRAPCMD HH3C-CFCARD-MIB::hh3cCfCardHotSwapOn HH3C-CFCARD-MIB::hh3cCfCardContainedIn i 0 HH3C-CFCARD-MIB::hh3cCfCardParentRelPos i 0 HH3C-CFCARD-MIB::hh3cCfCardDescription s EXAMPLE

description: The number of the slot which containes this CF Card
variables.name: HH3C-CFCARD-MIB::hh3cCfCardContainedIn

description: An indication of the relative position of this CF Card
among all the CF Card contained in the same slot.
variables.name: HH3C-CFCARD-MIB::hh3cCfCardParentRelPos

description: This notification is sent when a CF Card is hot swapped out.
objects.test: $SNMPTRAPCMD HH3C-CFCARD-MIB::hh3cCfCardHotSwapOff HH3C-CFCARD-MIB::hh3cCfCardContainedIn i 0 HH3C-CFCARD-MIB::hh3cCfCardParentRelPos i 0 HH3C-CFCARD-MIB::hh3cCfCardDescription s EXAMPLE

description: The number of the slot which containes this CF Card
variables.name: HH3C-CFCARD-MIB::hh3cCfCardContainedIn

description: An indication of the relative position of this CF Card
among all the CF Card contained in the same slot.
variables.name: HH3C-CFCARD-MIB::hh3cCfCardParentRelPos
